  "notes": "Live 2025-01 capture for inventory item staging, inventoryItems connection readback, explicit order inventory decrement at the real default inventory location, inventoryShipmentCreate accepting a carrier company label outside the old local allowlist, and inventoryTransfer read quantities after draft plus in-transit shipment consumption. The scenario uses captured disposable Shopify setup records and cassette-backed hydration; replayed mutations still stage locally without runtime Shopify writes."
